{"tid":1530481,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我哋係咪可以入去機場T1,T2？有關機場禁制令","createTime":"2019-09-02T03:27:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T09:39:38.000Z","uid":205710,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"66d2ed25fc06e33dd45101411fe4a751ed2db066","tid":1530481,"uid":205710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T03:27:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7MwK8JP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7MwK8JP.jpg&h=a101e53a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我想問機場個禁制令無話唔俾人入機場，佢只係話唔可以喺入面做某啲活動。咁如果強行進入T1,T2去算唔算違反禁制令呢？<br />\n而家係機管局單方面發出指引(<span style=\"color: red;\">上圖紅圈部份</span>)唔俾其他人進入去機場，如果我地強行進入，只不過係違反無法律約束力嘅機管局個<span style=\"color: red;\">指引</span>，因為果部份唔係禁制令一部份，咁算唔算違反禁制令？<br />\n<br />\n而我哋又可唔可以向法庭申請，阻止機管局個指引呢？<br />\n<br />\n求巴打解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7892d464000487051aadfd8628214cd9c4edfabf","tid":1530481,"uid":205710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T03:39:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"08deef65bc04544f466e15fbf2eaafcec535641d","tid":1530481,"uid":205710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T03:45:58.000Z","msg":"推啊，求巴打解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1458229cec4225573c927b372c00edb6997d15fa","tid":1530481,"uid":205710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T03:52:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f96881afcde4db092c2ea5ffb9341b1eb4a516c6","tid":1530481,"uid":205710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T04:04:52.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"0b2bf709c6bc9e7fbcdae643038be27730e9f6bd","tid":1530481,"uid":47222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T04:05:26.000Z","msg":"機場907 908戰術